# InkBytes monorepo (GitHub: pragmatalabs/InkBytes)
# Default-ignore everything at the root, then re-include the active v0 stack.
# Legacy/parked projects (Entopics, Unitas, Synochi, hermes, ...) keep their
# own nested .git repos and are intentionally NOT tracked by this monorepo.
/*
!.gitignore
!CLAUDE.md
!Messor/
!Curator/
!Reader/
!orchestrator/
!docs/

# ── Build / dependency / runtime junk (applies inside the tracked dirs) ──
node_modules/
.next/
.turbo/
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.so
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
*.tsbuildinfo

# ── Logs, data, runtime artifacts ──
*.log
logs/
*.sqlite3
data/scrapes/
data/history/
data/rabbit/
data/local/

# ── Secrets / local config (never commit) ──
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
env.local.yaml
*.local.yaml
.secrets.env

# ── OS / editor ──
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
.claude/settings.local.json
